I take this picture over any planned picture we have . Just to capture the effortless beauty she has takes my breath away . I capture every moment I fall more and more into her spell and she never notice , because I try to admire her when she's not looking so I won't look creepy just looking at her for no reason at all . At the end it never mattered on the amount of make up she wore or the clothes she had on but just the way she can sit in one spot long enough for me to realize a life without her unimagineable . üíëüíë
